  "img": "icons/environment/settlement/watchtower-city.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl315_LabelType\">Although you live some distance from the city-state your community owes fealty to, you&rsquo;ve been influenced by its sophisticated urban ways.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTraits_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Requirements</strong></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl315_LabelType\">Varisia</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl315_LabelType\">Determine the city-state of which your home is a holding. You gain a +1 trait bonus on checks with one Profession skill and one of the following benefits.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl315_LabelType\"><strong>Korvosa</strong></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl315_LabelType\">Gain Infernal as a bonus language. If you already have this language, gain a +1 trait bonus on Diplomacy checks.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl315_LabelType\">Magnimar</span></strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl315_LabelType\">Gain one random Varisian idol (see page 15 of&nbsp;</span><em>Varisia, Birthplace of Legends</em>).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl315_LabelType\">Riddleport</span></strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl315_LabelType\">Gain a +1 trait bonus on Swim checks.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Pathfinder Society</strong></p>\n<p>Magnimar not allowed.</p>",
